Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.82,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:743743,745828}Because he didn't.{NOTE:本当に似てないからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.45,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:745828,747455}How can you know?{NOTE:どうしてそんな事が分かるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.45,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:748748,750458}I met Hideyoshi.{NOTE:俺は秀吉に会った。}
