Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.50,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:751501,753503}You… met Hideyoshi?{NOTE:秀吉に…会った？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.09,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:759676,762095}Well, to be honest, my phrasing was off.{NOTE:と言うのは性格じゃねえな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:45.34,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:762095,765348}Strictly speaking, I met him in my previous life.{NOTE:正しくは前世の俺が会った。}
