Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:57.23,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:774649,777235}Before being born in modern age…{NOTE:現代に生まれる前は幕末の頃…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:13:00.57,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:777235,780571}…I plotted against the shogunate in the Satsuma Domain at the end of the Edo period.{NOTE:…薩摩藩で倒幕の士として働いていたらしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:05.82,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:780571,785827}Earlier than that, I was a strategist during Warring States period under Toyotomi Hideyoshi.{NOTE:さらにその前が安土桃山時代で豊臣秀吉の軍師だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:08.87,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:785827,788871}The famous siege of Odawara was my strategy.{NOTE:有名な小田原攻めは俺が立てた作戦だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:14.08,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:790915,794085}But nothing of it matters.{NOTE:ま、そんな事はどうでもいいさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:18.17,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:794085,798172}What matters is that I'm interested in Morio Megumi.{NOTE:とにかく俺は森尾めぐみが気に入ったってことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.13,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:798172,799132}Oh, wait.{NOTE:あ、待って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.92,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:802301,804929}Memories of previous lives…?{NOTE:前世のXX記憶があるなんて。}
