Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.77,0:35:18.57,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2114779,2118575}Toshiaki's memories will never come back again.{NOTE:俊明の六年間の記憶はもう二度と蘇らないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.90,0:35:21.16,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2119909,2121161}Seira.{NOTE:セイラ。}
Comment: 0,0:35:22.03,0:35:22.03,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:2122037,2122037}Chapter 9
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.32,0:35:26.29,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2122328,2126291}Still, Toshiaki Tsuzuki had lived for 16 years.{NOTE:それでも都築俊明は十六年間生きていたぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.83,0:35:32.00,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2128835,2132005}The lost memories will never come back…{NOTE:無くしてしまった思いは消して戻らないが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.00,0:35:35.09,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2132005,2135091}…but in exchange, there are a lot of new memories.{NOTE:…代わりに生まれてくる思いだってある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.09,0:35:37.92,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2135091,2137927}You should take good care of both and keep on living.{NOTE:どちらも大切にしてお前が生きていけばいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.22,0:35:41.72,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2140221,2141723}Kara.{NOTE:カラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.72,0:35:45.81,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2141723,2145810}Are you going to take us back to the 23rd century, to the spacetime police?{NOTE:俺達を23世紀の航時局へ連れて行くつもりか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.06,0:35:48.93,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2147062,2148936}Of course not.{NOTE:そんなこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.93,0:35:50.56,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2148936,2150565}I see.{NOTE:そうっか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.56,0:35:51.94,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2150565,2151941}Thank you, Kara.{NOTE:有難うカラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.19,0:35:54.31,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2153193,2154319}Stay safe.{NOTE:元気だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.19,0:35:58.28,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2157197,2158281}Taisa.{NOTE:タイサ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.41,0:36:09.41,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2167415,2169417}Seira.{NOTE:セイラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.41,0:36:11.37,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2169417,2171377}It's just like Taisa said.{NOTE:タイサの言う通りだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.37,0:36:13.63,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2171377,2173630}You can't regain lost memories…{NOTE:失くした思いは戻らないけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.63,0:36:15.71,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2173630,2175715}…but you can always make new ones.{NOTE:…代わりに生まれてくる思いもある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.42,0:36:20.13,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2177425,2180136}I want to cherish the lost memories.{NOTE:失くした思いを大切にしたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.13,0:36:23.76,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2180136,2183765}Everything's connected through the current me.{NOTE:全てがあって今の僕がいるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.76,0:36:25.72,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2183765,2185725}Seira.{NOTE:セイラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.10,0:36:30.85,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2188103,2190855}I'm glad I got to meet you.{NOTE:会えてよかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.85,0:36:32.06,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2190855,2192065}Kara.{NOTE:カラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.27,0:36:37.77,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2193274,2197779}I can clearly understand you now.{NOTE:私今ならセイラの思いがはっきり分かる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.77,0:36:38.86,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2197779,2198863}But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.86,0:36:40.53,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2198863,2200532}It's fine.{NOTE:いいんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.53,0:36:42.49,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2200532,2202492}I was able to see you again.{NOTE:君とこうして会えたんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.74,0:36:44.95,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2203743,2204953}I'm so happy.{NOTE:嬉しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.16,0:36:50.04,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2207163,2210041}I will never forget that I loved you.{NOTE:君を好きだったこと忘れないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.83,0:36:53.79,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2211835,2213795}Thank you, Seira.{NOTE:有難う、セイラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.89,0:37:09.18,Default,Kara,0,0,0,,{TIME:2226891,2229185}I'll love you forever.{NOTE:いつまでも大好き。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.90,0:37:21.53,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2239904,2241531}Kara.{NOTE:カラ。}
Comment: 0,0:37:27.45,0:37:27.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:2247454,2247454}Chapter 10
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.71,0:37:42.13,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2259716,2262135}I wonder if Kara's doing well.{NOTE:カラ元気でいるかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.13,0:37:42.88,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2262135,2262886}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.88,0:37:44.80,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2262886,2264804}She'll be fine.{NOTE:彼女なら大丈夫さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.80,0:37:46.97,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2264804,2266973}But Megumi is incredible.{NOTE:しかしめぐみは元気だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.97,0:37:49.72,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2266973,2269726}She acts the next day like nothing happened.{NOTE:あんなことがあった次の日けろっとして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.72,0:37:51.72,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2269726,2271726}She lets us listen to that brilliant flute play…{NOTE:見事なフルートを聞かせるんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.10,0:37:56.02,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2273104,2276024}Sorry. Looks like I won again.{NOTE:悪いな。又僕の勝ちで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.02,0:37:57.02,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2276024,2277025}Don't be stupid.{NOTE:バカ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.02,0:37:58.73,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2277025,2278735}Like I care.{NOTE:大きなお世話だ。}
