Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.86,0:38:02.53,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2279861,2282530}You can drop the tough act.{NOTE:強がりはやめたほうがいいぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.24,0:38:07.95,Default,Morio Megumi,0,0,0,,{TIME:2284240,2287952}Since when do they get along so well?{NOTE:あの二人いつのまに仲良くなったのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.53,0:38:12.66,Default,Tōno Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{TIME:2290538,2292665}You can get by wherever you are.{NOTE:どこだってやっていける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.66,0:38:15.91,Default,Tsuzuki Toshiaki,0,0,0,,{TIME:2292665,2295919}There's place for everything in this wide world.{NOTE:この広い世界きっとどこまでもな。}
